								<node id="editorData">
									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Apart from Minthara, who stands closer to the player, the companions look on horrified. The black fog of the mindmelds and absolutes scenes flow from the player.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The companions struggle to stand in the presence of the New Absolute. Their squints turn into blinks, which reveal their eyes have changed to glow mind flayer orange. Their movements calm, as the black fog dissipates.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The player makes a fist and off screen we hear the sounds of the companions transforming into illithids off-screen. Astarion is spared." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
