											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Dragons and Nautiloids still fight around the the skies of Baldur's Gate.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The player closes their eyes focusing.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Arcs of electricity sprout from the base of the throne across the massive zepplin-like form of the Netherbrain. Energy is built up, until a shockwave is released.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;As the dragons are caught in blast, they fall from the sky to the streets below, breathing their last licks of remaining fire." />
